data.description: LOCATION LOCATION!!! This two-family which features, Unit 1: 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, Living Room, EIK, and den (possible 3rd bedroom) and Unit 2: 3 Bedrooms, 1 bathroom, Living Room, EIK. Full unfinished basement with walk-out to back and washer/dryer hook-ups. Brand new furnaces and all separate utilities. Just one block from Garfield Light Rail Station, A few blocks from Liberty State Park, NJ Turnpike and in one of the most up and coming neighborhoods in Jersey City, you will want to come check this home out! Month-to-month tenants. Live in one unit and rent out the other or use as investment and build/add to your portfolio. Schedule your private viewing today!
